            <p class="text-[15px] text-slate-600 m-0">
              Every request signed with HMAC-SHA256. Verify that requests to your endpoint actually came from Runlater.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 bg-emerald-600 rounded-md flex items-center justify-center">
            <.icon name="hero-key" class="w-4 h-4 text-white" />
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold mb-1 text-slate-900">Idempotency</h3>
            <p class="text-[15px] text-slate-600 m-0">
              Pass an idempotency key and we guarantee exactly-once task creation. Safe to retry from your client without duplicates.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 bg-emerald-600 rounded-md flex items-center justify-center">
            <.icon name="hero-funnel" class="w-4 h-4 text-white" />
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold mb-1 text-slate-900">Deduplication</h3>
            <p class="text-[15px] text-slate-600 m-0">
              Idempotency keys prevent duplicate tasks. Retry the same request safely — we'll return the original result, not create a new task.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 bg-emerald-600 rounded-md flex items-center justify-center">
            <.icon name="hero-adjustments-horizontal" class="w-4 h-4 text-white" />
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold mb-1 text-slate-900">Custom headers and payloads</h3>
            <p class="text-[15px] text-slate-600 m-0">
              Send any HTTP method, headers, and request body. Forward webhooks, trigger APIs, authenticate with your own tokens.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 bg-emerald-600 rounded-md flex items-center justify-center">
            <.icon name="hero-document-text" class="w-4 h-4 text-white" />
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold mb-1 text-slate-900">Full execution history</h3>
            <p class="text-[15px] text-slate-600 m-0">
              Every run logged with status code, duration, and response body. Debug failures without digging through your own logs.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 bg-emerald-600 rounded-md flex items-center justify-center">
            <.icon name="hero-bell-alert" class="w-4 h-4 text-white" />
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold mb-1 text-slate-900">Alerts to Slack, Discord, or email</h3>
            <p class="text-[15px] text-slate-600 m-0">
              Get notified only when something fails. We auto-detect Slack and Discord webhook URLs and format the message for you.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

<!-- How it works -->
    <section class="py-14 border-t border-slate-200">
      <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400 mb-8">
        How it works
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <%!-- Step 1 --%>
        <div class="glass-card rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
          <div class="px-5 py-3 border-b border-slate-200/60 flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-6 h-6 bg-emerald-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-xs font-bold">1</span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 m-0">Delay a task</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 m-0">Something happened, do this in 24 hours</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <pre phx-no-curly-interpolation class="bg-slate-900 text-slate-100 p-4 sm:p-5 font-mono text-xs sm:text-sm leading-relaxed overflow-x-auto m-0 rounded-none">curl -X POST https://runlater.eu/api/v1/tasks \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer pk_live_xxx" \
  -H "Idempotency-Key: reminder-user-42" \
  -d '{
    <span class="text-sky-300">"url"</span>: <span class="text-green-300">"https://myapp.com/api/remind"</span>,
    <span class="text-sky-300">"delay"</span>: <span class="text-green-300">"24h"</span>
  }'</pre>
        </div>

        <%!-- Step 2 --%>
        <div class="glass-card rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
          <div class="px-5 py-3 border-b border-slate-200/60 flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-6 h-6 bg-emerald-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-xs font-bold">2</span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 m-0">Queue a task</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 m-0">Offload work from your request cycle</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <pre phx-no-curly-interpolation class="bg-slate-900 text-slate-100 p-4 sm:p-5 font-mono text-xs sm:text-sm leading-relaxed overflow-x-auto m-0 rounded-none">curl -X POST https://runlater.eu/api/v1/tasks \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer pk_live_xxx" \
  -d '{
    <span class="text-sky-300">"url"</span>: <span class="text-green-300">"https://myapp.com/api/process"</span>,
    <span class="text-sky-300">"queue"</span>: <span class="text-green-300">"payments"</span>,
    <span class="text-sky-300">"callback_url"</span>: <span class="text-green-300">"https://myapp.com/api/done"</span>
  }'</pre>
        </div>

        <%!-- Step 3 --%>
        <div class="glass-card rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
          <div class="px-5 py-3 border-b border-slate-200/60 flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-6 h-6 bg-emerald-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-xs font-bold">3</span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 m-0">Schedule a cron</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 m-0">Recurring jobs on any schedule</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <pre phx-no-curly-interpolation class="bg-slate-900 text-slate-100 p-4 sm:p-5 font-mono text-xs sm:text-sm leading-relaxed overflow-x-auto m-0 rounded-none">curl -X POST https://runlater.eu/api/v1/tasks \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer pk_live_xxx" \
  -d '{
    <span class="text-sky-300">"name"</span>: <span class="text-green-300">"Daily backup"</span>,
    <span class="text-sky-300">"url"</span>: <span class="text-green-300">"https://myapp.com/api/backup"</span>,
    <span class="text-sky-300">"cron"</span>: <span class="text-green-300">"0 6 * * *"</span>
  }'</pre>
        </div>

        <p class="text-center text-sm text-slate-500 pt-2">
          That's it. We handle retries, callbacks, and alerts.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

